<br>
I kinda want to turn this into a brainstorm thread as it were. So lets try not to bash other peoples ideas.<br>
<br>
And yes Ichi, TLC was removed from all production servers except FV. After presenting Verant with all of our arguements pointing out the bad points of the TLC outwerighed the good points, Verant decided to poll the players. The poll showed the majority of the players were against TLC, so verant removed the code from all of SoL and went back and removed it from Stonebrunt and the warrens.<br>
<br>
I think if were gonna keep some form of TLC on FV, we need to be able to give Verant some ideas. So lets hear em!<br>
