Everyone who has posted that they hate TLC has never realy stated a good enuff reason in my mind to have it removed.  Untail somone states a good enuff reason that would cause verant to rethink TLC nothing is going to change about it.  As to it making quests harder if you level past them?  Guess what verant dosn't care, they say it's your own fault if you level past a quest, find someone to help you with it.  Also Verant is of the opinion that we as players are not ENTITLED to every item and quest.  There are so many things in this game to aquire that verant won't change a rule just so you can get one harder to get item.  If an item IS proven to be imposible for anyone to get submit that to verant and im certain they'd do something about making that one item possible to get.<br>
